---
title: Frequently Asked Questions
description: Got questions about Land Shark Tours in Santa Barbara? Find answers about tour length, tickets, accessibility, parking, weather cancellations, and more.
keywords: Land Shark Tours FAQ, Santa Barbara amphibious tour questions, Land Shark Tours tickets, Santa Barbara tour accessibility, public tour questions Santa Barbara
---

{% extends "layouts/base.njk" %}

{% block content %}
  <section class="py-12 px-4 mx-auto max-w-screen-xl lg:px-6">
    <div class="max-w-3xl">
      <h1 class="mb-4 text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
      <p class="mb-10 text-lg font-light text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">For Public Tours</p>

      <div class="space-y-8">

        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-2 text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">How long is the tour?</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Approximately 90 minutes, half on land, half at sea.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-2 text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Do we have to stop and wait for people to get on and off during the tour?</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">No, tours are nonstop fun!</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-2 text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Is there a guide on board?</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Yes, every public tour is narrated with an amazing award winning tour guide.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-2 text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Are there restrooms on board?</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">No, restrooms are available at the departure and return location before and after every tour.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-2 text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Are babies free?</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Yes, there is no charge for children under the age of 2 if they are seated in your lap.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-2 text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Is there stroller or wheelchair storage?</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Yes, the crew may bring it on board or lock and store it at the departure location.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-2 text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Where do I get tickets?</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Tickets can be purchased online or there are a limited number of non-advance seats available for purchase as you board — first come, first serve. Cash and credit cards are accepted.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-2 text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Can I make a reservation?</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Yes, tour tickets can be purchased online. Advance ticket inquiries can be made via email to <a href="mailto:LandAndSeaTours@aol.com" class="text-blue-700 hover:underline dark:text-blue-500">LandAndSeaTours@aol.com</a>.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-2 text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Can we bring food or drinks?</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Food and alcoholic beverages are not permitted on public tours.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-2 text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">How early should I arrive?</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">At least 15 minutes prior to departure. Allow more time for large groups and during holidays.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-2 text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">What should I wear?</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Bring a jacket or sweatshirt — it may be cooler while at sea.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-2 text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Do the tours run in bad weather?</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">The captain may cancel tours at any time if hazardous conditions are present.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-2 text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Is it easy to get on board?</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Yes, there are seven steps with handrails on either side. Crewmembers are able to assist all passengers during boarding and disembarking.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-2 text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Will I get seasick?</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">No.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-2 text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">How many seats are available on each tour?</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">40 people.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-2 text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Is there parking nearby?</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Yes, street parking on Cabrillo Blvd and Chapala St., and on Stearns Wharf.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-2 text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Are there discounts?</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Discounts are not available.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-2 text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Can I book a private tour?</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Yes, please see our <a href="{{ "/charter/" | url }}" class="text-blue-700 hover:underline dark:text-blue-500">private charter page</a> for more information.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-2 text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Are gift certificates available?</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Yes, gift certificates can be purchased over the phone or on board. You can also <a href="{{ "/gift-cards/" | url }}" class="text-blue-700 hover:underline dark:text-blue-500">purchase gift cards online</a>.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-2 text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Can we feed the sharks?</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Yes, only on land at the end of the tour.</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
{% endblock %}
